section.section:
The cabinet shall:
Provide leadership in water use efficiency for all water uses;
Promote conservation;
Offer technical assistance and conduct research;
Be the lead agency with other state and local agencies to incorporate conservation measures and incentives into their programs;
Sponsor "technology transfer sessions" on water conservation to commercial and industrial operations; and
Provide leadership to communities looking for information and methods for coping with the issues of growth and water supply.
